00:15:38.420 --> 00:15:42.700
[Guest]: And city planners are going to say how tall buildings are going to be.

00:15:42.700 --> 00:15:45.900
[Guest]: They're going to say what buildings should be built where.

00:15:45.900 --> 00:15:48.380
[Guest]: You know, these should only be residences.

00:15:48.380 --> 00:15:49.580
[Guest]: These should only be factories.

00:15:49.580 --> 00:15:51.500
[Guest]: They're going to try and plan everything.

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:54.220
[Guest]: And of course, that has worked out to be a disaster in practice.

00:15:54.220 --> 00:15:56.860
